latestPosts.caption:
🚀 PROMPT 1
You have 20 years of experience as a fitness coach. I want you to make me a diet plan for losing weight. I am 20 years old living in India. Height is 5 feet 10 inches and I weigh 88 kg.  My target weight is 75 kg and I want to lose 3kg per month. I am a student so I have a limited budget. The protein sources available are egg, paneer, tofu, soy chunks, daal and beans in abundance and I can get access to chicken once per week. And commonly available carb sources are brown bread, rolled oats (quaker) and rice. Suggest recipes that are simple to make. I want to eat at least 100g of protein daily. 

🚀 PROMPT 2
Now mention the macros and calories in each dish and also mention the total macros and calories for the day

🚀 PROMPT 3
Create a grocery list for me according to the meal plan above and categorize it in protein, carbs, fats and fiber
.
.
.
#smart #ai #fitness #planner #strategy #diet #dietplan #fitnessplan

⏳️ ONE YEAR Apart ------>

First photo - July 2017 - 18 yrs old
Second Photo - Nov 2018 - 19 yes old

I was a 2nd year student when I started my Transformation journey. I did not know if I would have a good physique when I start but I knew one thing that training is a part of life and is one of the highest priorities. 

Its been 8 years. I'm still going strong. Even today when I drift off my path, or get lazy and start eating junk or focus too much on my fat percentage levels, I look back and see where I started from. It really sets things in perspective for me.

Keep Hustling💪
.
.
.
#transformation #journey #consistency

⛳️ Not everything online is what it seems
Ever scroll through Instagram feeling like everyone else has the perfect body?  You're not alone!  Social media is filled with carefully curated snapshots , often with unrealistic expectations.

⛳️ The truth is, many physiques you see online take hours of editing  and dedication that most people just don't have . It's okay to have a little body fat (we all do!), and it's okay not to look "beach ready" all the time! ️ Our worth isn't defined by how we look in a filtered photo

⛳️ Let's break free from unrealistic beauty standards  and celebrate real bodies in all their glory!  What are your thoughts? 

#bodypositivity #ditchthefilte #reality #loveyourself #selflovejourney #strongnotskinny #mybodymytemple #allbodiesaregoodbodies #realbeauty #bodyacceptance #effyourbeautystandards #pkfitness #fitness #motivation #mentalhealth #positivity

It is quite difficult to sustain a peak physique 100% of the time. It is ok if you don't look at your peak all the time, it is perfectly normal!

Nevertheless, strive to be at your best whenever you can so you feel good mentally. Those who workout regularly kniw that this is a mental game! Good luck.

Keep hustling💪

#pkfinesshub #transformation #physique #bodybuilding #viral #pkfinesshub #gymmotivation #motivation #fitness #fitnessmotivation

⛳️ You have to do whatever you can to achieve your goals. Do not be the one who finds excuses to not do things. Instead think of the way you can. 

🧠 Your brain is powerful, if health is important to you, you will find a way even when it seems difficult!
